WEBVTT

00:00.164 --> 00:02.648
Your wife... nobody's
seen or heard from her

00:02.714 --> 00:04.346
in two and a half months.

00:07.613 --> 00:10.445
I <i> will</i> find out
what you did to her.

00:10.573 --> 00:13.156
- How much you want, Javi?
- 300 Grand.

00:13.231 --> 00:15.156
I'm sorry, smurf.

00:16.645 --> 00:20.039
♪♪

00:22.456 --> 00:25.191
You think I came all this way
for 25 Grand? Huh?!

00:25.806 --> 00:28.595
For the last Goddamn time,
where's the real money?!

00:28.633 --> 00:31.173
- I swear!
- How'd you hurt your leg? Eh?

00:33.439 --> 00:34.971
No!

00:35.946 --> 00:38.313
- Nicky.
- Who took Nicky, J?

00:38.417 --> 00:40.330
- Javi.
- Aah!

00:41.472 --> 00:43.339
Tell me where you are.
We'll come get you.

00:43.372 --> 00:45.080
Trailhead
and... and ash.

00:45.141 --> 00:46.874
- It's where we buried him.
- Who?

00:46.914 --> 00:48.447
Javi's father.

00:49.285 --> 00:52.556
♪♪

00:52.716 --> 00:58.259
♪ She stares deeply ♪

00:58.330 --> 01:02.236
♪ locked inside me ♪

01:02.370 --> 01:05.638
♪ burnin' brightly ♪

01:05.662 --> 01:07.908
♪♪

01:07.932 --> 01:10.283
♪♪

01:10.422 --> 01:13.938
♪ One they know
that I cannot take ♪

01:14.078 --> 01:17.345
♪ waitin' for it all to begin ♪

01:17.434 --> 01:21.228
♪ every night now, they'll win ♪

01:21.252 --> 01:24.533
♪♪

01:24.729 --> 01:27.205
♪ Come and meet my black hole ♪

01:27.340 --> 01:31.025
♪ got a big black hole ♪

01:31.112 --> 01:34.931
♪ got a big black hole ♪

