03:19.037 --> 03:20.478
Working on a yacht?

03:20.701 --> 03:23.506
I tell you what, you're gonna
make the world's worst waiter.

03:24.417 --> 03:25.975
Then I'll bartend.

03:28.423 --> 03:30.857
<i>♪♪</i>

03:31.935 --> 03:33.524
You kidding me with this?

03:35.983 --> 03:37.410
Smurf again.

03:38.060 --> 03:39.419
Yeah.

03:39.748 --> 03:41.832
So as soon as we get
the schedule,

03:42.068 --> 03:44.735
we pick the party
with the highest rollers.

03:44.896 --> 03:46.928
I'll do the few events,
see what we find.

03:47.073 --> 03:48.326
Yeah.

03:48.522 --> 03:51.452
Just make sure you don't get
your ass fired on the first day.

03:51.935 --> 03:53.904
So what's up? Are we gonna
need everybody on this?

03:53.928 --> 03:55.089
I'm on the inside.

03:55.279 --> 03:56.889
I'll kill the engine
and the radio.

03:57.076 --> 03:59.123
You three with guns
to fleece the guests.

03:59.357 --> 04:01.482
Someone else to distract
the coast guard.

04:03.268 --> 04:04.989
<i>♪♪</i>

04:05.240 --> 04:07.325
Don't even bother with that.
She's looking for me.

04:07.545 --> 04:08.689
"9-1-1"?

04:08.761 --> 04:10.678
Yeah, she probably forgot
the Wi-Fi password.

04:10.842 --> 04:12.936
Why is she so pissed
at you?

04:13.433 --> 04:14.965
It's the same old shit.

04:15.162 --> 04:17.401
When mama calls, just throw
the phone in the fridge.

04:18.706 --> 04:20.426
Problem solved.

04:20.490 --> 04:22.707
Yo, we keep this job
between us till we're solid.

04:22.809 --> 04:24.433
- Yeah, I'm cool with that.
- All right.

04:26.762 --> 04:28.746
<i>- Hey, it's Deran.
- Leave a message.</i>

04:29.815 --> 04:32.136
Go get your brothers!

04:34.433 --> 04:36.433
I can handle it here.

04:37.582 --> 04:40.871
Turn on the perimeter alarm.
Watch the cameras.

04:52.738 --> 04:56.160
You feel better, baby?
Let me get you some ice packs.

04:56.746 --> 04:58.409
How do I find Javi?

04:58.722 --> 05:00.354
Take a deep breath.

05:01.527 --> 05:04.840
J, what you're feeling now
is shame.

05:06.284 --> 05:08.543
There were four of them.

05:08.972 --> 05:10.933
There was nothing
you could do.

05:11.129 --> 05:12.423
Nothing.

05:14.436 --> 05:17.527
♪♪

05:33.800 --> 05:35.003
Get in.

05:37.904 --> 05:39.071
You okay?

05:39.962 --> 05:41.312
You talk to anyone?

05:41.612 --> 05:43.175
Did you call anyone?

05:43.526 --> 05:44.894
Did you call anyone?

05:45.026 --> 05:47.354
- No, it... uh, just... just smurf.
- Good.

05:47.838 --> 05:49.738
You understand why we can't go
to the cops, right?

05:49.762 --> 05:50.925
- All right?
- Yeah.

05:50.979 --> 05:52.479
Did they hurt you?

05:55.338 --> 05:56.408
Hey.

05:56.473 --> 05:58.659
You're safe now. Okay?

06:02.126 --> 06:04.318
- I gave them your number.
- Who?

06:04.734 --> 06:07.540
I-I... the... the guy in charge.
He... he had a gun.

06:08.947 --> 06:11.383
- It's okay.
- I'm sorry.

06:11.516 --> 06:13.071
It's all right.

06:22.797 --> 06:24.464
J?

06:35.029 --> 06:36.818
Hey.

06:38.325 --> 06:40.154
Who were those guys?

06:45.693 --> 06:47.381
Did they hurt you?

06:48.076 --> 06:50.217
No, he just put a...

06:50.334 --> 06:52.748
He had a knife
to my neck, but they didn't...

06:52.959 --> 06:54.825
They didn't do anything.

06:56.306 --> 06:57.967
I'm sorry, j.

06:58.845 --> 07:02.678
♪♪

07:11.906 --> 07:13.077
Okay.

07:14.578 --> 07:16.507
It's okay.
You feeling better?

07:16.640 --> 07:18.101
Yeah.

07:19.875 --> 07:22.476
You know we're never gonna let
anything happen to you.

07:22.686 --> 07:24.617
You know that, don't you?

07:25.891 --> 07:27.056
Thank you.

07:27.164 --> 07:29.820
I need to talk to j
for a minute.

07:30.398 --> 07:31.958
Why don't you go take
a nice hot shower,

07:31.998 --> 07:35.421
and I'll have Craig bring you
some oxys, okay?

07:35.851 --> 07:38.882
- Okay.
- Thank you, baby.

07:41.739 --> 07:44.324
J, let's go.

07:50.377 --> 07:52.549
♪♪

07:52.752 --> 07:55.408
Pope fill you in on
what happened?

07:56.634 --> 07:58.338
What's Javi got on you?

07:58.541 --> 08:02.002
Uh, Luis was this dude...
He was Javi's father...

08:02.096 --> 08:04.260
And he used to run
with Manny and I.

08:04.439 --> 08:07.765
We pulled a bank job.
It was supposed to be super easy.

08:07.877 --> 08:09.867
But we had
an unexpected visitor.

08:09.947 --> 08:12.846
We had a hero
with a concealed 0.45.

08:13.033 --> 08:15.463
Hero fires, hits Lou in the gut.

08:15.588 --> 08:19.143
Lou has a shotgun,
takes hero's head off.

08:19.588 --> 08:22.471
But Lou's already bleeding out
from the gut wound

08:22.580 --> 08:25.293
and, uh, he's not gonna make it,
hospital or no.

08:25.447 --> 08:28.111
So Manny just put him
out of his misery.

08:30.674 --> 08:33.134
And then we drove the body
to a construction site

08:33.205 --> 08:36.432
that... I don't know,
someone just knew

08:36.486 --> 08:40.057
they were pouring the foundation
for a house the next day.

08:40.529 --> 08:42.195
We buried him under it.

08:42.962 --> 08:45.041
You told us Lou ran off
with the money.

08:45.182 --> 08:47.603
Javi is threatening to go
to the police

08:47.666 --> 08:49.705
and let them know
where the body is.

08:49.830 --> 08:51.846
So pay him.
I tried.

08:52.092 --> 08:56.018
How much does he want?
He wants $300k.

08:56.580 --> 09:01.150
Except Jake put a gun in my face
and took off with my money.

09:01.205 --> 09:03.143
Why the hell would you
trust Jake?

09:03.322 --> 09:05.400
I didn't have any options,
did I?

09:05.560 --> 09:07.360
Where'd you get 300k?

09:07.573 --> 09:09.239
My savings.

09:14.385 --> 09:15.838
You think he's coming back?

09:15.968 --> 09:17.869
Nah, he's gotta know
we'd be waiting for him.

09:18.104 --> 09:20.502
So what if the cops find
the body?

09:20.940 --> 09:23.252
It's been 20 years
it's been in the ground.

09:23.541 --> 09:25.908
And this... this Manny guy's
the one who shot him, so why...

09:25.971 --> 09:27.666
With <i> my</i> gun.

09:28.080 --> 09:29.791
He tossed it in with the body

09:29.869 --> 09:31.627
and told me about it
the next day.

09:31.793 --> 09:33.326
Too late to do anything.

09:33.502 --> 09:37.041
The cops can link you
to the gun?

09:37.893 --> 09:39.189
Yep.

09:40.446 --> 09:42.955
So what do you want us
to do about it?

09:44.533 --> 09:46.330
We have to deal with Javi.

09:46.619 --> 09:48.532
- Deal with him?
- Yes.

09:48.573 --> 09:50.220
You were gonna pay him
this afternoon.

09:50.259 --> 09:52.369
- Just pay him now.
- Yeah, Nicky gave him my number.

09:52.393 --> 09:55.799
If he reaches out, maybe there's
still a way we can negotiate.

09:56.205 --> 09:58.713
This has gone way past that now.

09:58.799 --> 10:01.679
For <i> you,</i> it's gone
way past that. Not for us.

10:03.010 --> 10:05.816
They almost killed J.

10:06.072 --> 10:07.478
But they didn't.

10:08.299 --> 10:09.687
He's all right.

10:10.189 --> 10:13.268
And what do you want us
to do exactly? Huh?

10:13.495 --> 10:16.137
What, you want us to hunt down
this guy with assault rifles

10:16.252 --> 10:19.635
for some bullshit that <i> you</i> did
that has nothing to do with us?

10:19.853 --> 10:22.471
Do you have any idea what
your life would've been like

10:22.619 --> 10:26.361
if I took a murder rap
when you were 5 years old?

10:26.830 --> 10:28.189
Yeah, well, you know what?

10:28.244 --> 10:30.124
Foster care would've been
better than this shit.

10:30.334 --> 10:32.002
You think so?

10:32.377 --> 10:34.268
I'll tell you about it
sometime.

10:36.322 --> 10:38.877
Well, J,
looks like your uncles

10:38.947 --> 10:41.262
don't really give a damn
about you, does it?

10:41.455 --> 10:42.720
Nobody's saying that, smurf.

10:42.752 --> 10:44.365
You're saying
that a group of people

10:44.432 --> 10:46.353
can come into <i> our</i> house

10:46.425 --> 10:48.665
and beat the shit
out of him.

10:48.821 --> 10:50.926
We're trying to figure it out.
No one is saying that.

10:50.950 --> 10:53.478
If that were you lying there
by the pool...

10:53.557 --> 10:54.869
Yeah.

10:55.009 --> 10:56.947
Would we even be having
this conversation?

10:57.049 --> 10:59.143
We don't just kill people.

11:01.127 --> 11:04.127
I mean, I'm not finishing
this conversation with her here,

11:04.174 --> 11:07.478
so let's
figure this out on our own.

11:07.627 --> 11:11.502
♪♪

11:12.166 --> 11:15.377
Just remember, Javi is not
a little kid anymore.

11:15.822 --> 11:18.655
He's angry and unstable.

11:19.174 --> 11:22.626
This doesn't end until
we end it.

11:27.569 --> 11:29.503
Make up your minds.

11:31.577 --> 11:35.314
♪♪

11:40.638 --> 11:42.632
Yeah, he's... he's been
following her

11:42.727 --> 11:44.671
and threatening her ever since
Manny's funeral.

11:44.734 --> 11:46.377
And you didn't say <i> shit?</i>

11:46.616 --> 11:47.991
She asked me not to.

11:48.031 --> 11:49.348
You probably should've
shot his ass

11:49.372 --> 11:50.702
when he was in
the Goddamn house.

11:50.795 --> 11:52.186
'Cause then maybe we could say
it was self-defense.

11:52.210 --> 11:54.179
- Deran.
- What?

11:54.999 --> 11:57.515
I'm just sayin',
if any of us had been here,

11:57.540 --> 11:58.617
we wouldn't be having
this problem right now.

11:58.641 --> 12:01.077
- I'm sorry.
- What the hell was I supposed to do?!

12:01.319 --> 12:03.663
- Come on! Four guys with guns...
- Yes.

12:03.702 --> 12:04.986
- Hey. Hey!
- All by myself!

12:05.010 --> 12:06.131
Yes, that is what you do
in that...

12:06.156 --> 12:07.960
- situation.
- Hey, leave the kid alone.

12:08.499 --> 12:10.007
I'm not killing for her, pope.

12:10.053 --> 12:11.619
And you don't have to.

12:11.921 --> 12:13.311
All right?

12:13.999 --> 12:16.784
- We call the shots now.
- Yeah, he's right.

12:17.077 --> 12:20.225
Look at her.
She thinks we'll do it.

12:20.250 --> 12:22.090
She thinks we'll do anything
for her.

12:25.943 --> 12:27.483
And I'll tell you one thing...

12:27.557 --> 12:29.483
I'm not doing life in prison

12:29.632 --> 12:32.382
for some 20-year-old bullshit
that has nothing to do with me.

12:32.608 --> 12:33.640
Me neither.

12:33.772 --> 12:36.684
We move the body,
we take the leverage.

12:36.991 --> 12:39.343
I saw the neighborhood
when I picked up Nicky.

12:39.515 --> 12:41.322
We gotta get around
the homeowners.

12:41.452 --> 12:42.662
We've done riskier jobs.

12:42.734 --> 12:45.624
Man, I-I-I steal shit
for money.

12:45.702 --> 12:47.647
- I don't kill people for old debts.
- Guys, if she goes down for this,

12:47.671 --> 12:49.615
- she could bring all of us down with her.
- She won't flip.

12:49.639 --> 12:51.343
- What is wrong with you? - Give me a break. - She won't!

12:51.367 --> 12:53.211
What is wrong with you, pope?
I thought you hated her.

12:53.235 --> 12:54.820
No one in this family is
going to prison...

12:54.844 --> 12:55.873
Oh, yeah? Not if they don't have to.

12:55.897 --> 12:56.949
When you went to prison,
she was relieved.

12:56.950 --> 12:58.749
- She was relieved.
- Dude, shut up!

13:00.868 --> 13:02.587
She's not going to prison.

13:11.564 --> 13:13.289
I'm trying.

13:18.894 --> 13:20.828
So?

13:23.813 --> 13:25.884
We're not killing anyone.
We're gonna move the body.

13:26.002 --> 13:27.126
What?

13:27.271 --> 13:29.251
He can't threaten you
if he doesn't have anything.

13:29.407 --> 13:30.727
We're gonna move the body.

13:30.837 --> 13:32.806
J's gonna be pissing blood
for weeks.

13:32.884 --> 13:34.975
This isn't just about
leverage.

13:35.064 --> 13:36.931
That's the best
you're gonna get.

13:37.665 --> 13:39.274
And when he comes back?

13:39.454 --> 13:41.649
<i>If</i> he comes back,
we will deal with it.

13:42.016 --> 13:44.212
And you have to pay them.
Pay who?

13:44.391 --> 13:47.220
Deran and Craig want to be
paid for their services.

13:52.321 --> 13:55.516
I'm paying my sons
to keep me out of prison?

14:02.415 --> 14:04.118
Do I have a choice?

14:05.102 --> 14:06.977
- No.
- No.

14:09.923 --> 14:12.446
That's a nice way
to run things, baz.

14:12.875 --> 14:14.587
Try and get some rest.

14:16.618 --> 14:20.384
♪♪

14:23.814 --> 14:26.274
Hey, hang back a minute.
I gotta talk to you.

14:27.047 --> 14:28.616
I need you to take point
on this one.

14:28.704 --> 14:31.688
Oh, she's just trying to get in my head.
No, man, listen.

14:33.376 --> 14:35.102
I got pulled over
this afternoon.

14:36.923 --> 14:39.212
Yeah, I'm trying to stay calm,
and the guy,

14:39.376 --> 14:41.610
he starts asking me
about Cath.

14:42.407 --> 14:45.431
And he says he's gonna find out
what I did to her.

14:47.102 --> 14:49.774
Man, she had a bank account
she never told me about.

14:50.298 --> 14:52.821
She hasn't touched it
since she left.

14:53.673 --> 14:55.602
- Jesus.
- Yeah.

14:56.470 --> 14:57.887
Anyway, I can't go near
the body.

14:57.915 --> 15:00.141
I-I'm not sure if
they're watching me or not.

15:01.766 --> 15:03.266
Yeah.

15:04.157 --> 15:05.933
Yeah, okay.

15:10.306 --> 15:12.239
The cops think she's dead.

15:15.516 --> 15:17.243
What do you think?

15:20.110 --> 15:21.915
Yeah, I think she's dead.

15:34.273 --> 15:36.477
Hey.

15:36.666 --> 15:38.532
Hi.

15:39.290 --> 15:41.368
Oh. Thanks.

15:45.141 --> 15:47.016
Should've been here.

15:48.149 --> 15:50.001
I'm sorry.

15:57.056 --> 15:58.946
Beer?

15:59.188 --> 16:00.876
Oh, no.

16:01.704 --> 16:04.688
You know what?
I'm... I'm kinda tired.

16:06.220 --> 16:07.727
Yeah. Uh...

16:07.915 --> 16:09.243
Okay.

16:10.024 --> 16:12.524
- I'll come and check on you later.
- Mm-hmm.

16:23.938 --> 16:27.485
Thanks. How's she doing?

16:30.438 --> 16:32.486
You think they're gonna
come back?

16:32.688 --> 16:35.641
Nah, not tonight.

16:36.649 --> 16:38.751
Pope's been walking around
with that shotgun.

16:38.970 --> 16:41.291
What, you think they would've
killed smurf if she was here?

16:43.610 --> 16:46.100
That's why he's got
the shotgun.

16:51.868 --> 16:54.441
Hey. I'm gonna take
the couch tonight.

16:54.735 --> 16:56.944
Smurf gave j my room.

16:57.485 --> 16:59.556
I'll sleep with Lena.

17:18.040 --> 17:20.200
So, look, did Javi say
anything else to you?

17:20.313 --> 17:23.681
Um, anything you can tell us
that would help us?

17:23.734 --> 17:24.845
Anything at all?

17:24.906 --> 17:28.234
Smurf was supposed to pay them,
but didn't show.

17:28.626 --> 17:30.891
They came here looking
for money.

17:31.570 --> 17:33.102
What'd you tell 'em?

17:35.290 --> 17:36.950
They had Nicky
in the other room.

17:37.337 --> 17:39.806
I told them there was cash
behind the dryer.

17:40.587 --> 17:41.989
That's good.

17:43.808 --> 17:45.742
You should've told them sooner.

17:47.891 --> 17:49.863
Don't let smurf get you killed.

17:50.462 --> 17:52.065
You played it right, man.

17:52.251 --> 17:55.502
If you'd come out shootin', you
and Nicky would both be dead.

17:58.712 --> 18:00.441
Get some sleep.

18:19.345 --> 18:21.931
You know, I expected
this halfway bullshit

18:22.024 --> 18:24.198
from your brothers,
but you?

18:25.509 --> 18:27.935
A cop stopped baz
this afternoon.

18:28.821 --> 18:31.001
They think he killed Cath.

18:31.507 --> 18:34.942
♪♪

18:51.493 --> 18:53.793
- Smurf up?
- I don't know.

18:57.223 --> 18:58.840
You've been sitting here
all night?

18:58.892 --> 19:02.114
We need the concrete saw
and the sledgehammers back.

19:02.708 --> 19:04.153
Okay.

19:04.611 --> 19:06.744
You get the truck?

19:07.004 --> 19:09.403
Yeah, I talked to Nico.
We're all good.

19:12.528 --> 19:15.176
This is how it starts,
you know?

19:16.049 --> 19:19.262
We do this for her,
next thing you know,

19:19.324 --> 19:21.713
we're right back here,
and she's running shit.

19:22.465 --> 19:24.121
Get the tools.

19:25.399 --> 19:27.801
Anybody want scrambled eggs?

19:28.738 --> 19:31.332
How was the couch? Okay?

19:32.586 --> 19:34.113
I'll see you in a couple hours.

19:34.223 --> 19:36.553
Could you take Nicky and j
with you?

19:38.145 --> 19:39.564
Javi's not coming back.

19:39.754 --> 19:43.435
I know, but I-i don't think
they should be here alone.

19:51.105 --> 19:52.793
We leave in five.

20:01.821 --> 20:03.081
Come here.

20:03.264 --> 20:06.683
Ally said she'd take you
to the beach. Okay?

20:06.855 --> 20:08.151
Here you go.

20:09.717 --> 20:11.097
Hey.

20:11.601 --> 20:13.042
Come here.

20:13.667 --> 20:15.151
Come here.

20:15.802 --> 20:17.370
I'm gonna be back tomorrow,
okay?

20:17.507 --> 20:19.558
- Okay.
- Okay.

20:21.448 --> 20:23.141
I've been gone
a lot, right?

20:25.972 --> 20:27.972
It's okay. You can say it.

20:28.319 --> 20:29.393
Yeah.

20:29.506 --> 20:31.082
Okay, we'll do something
together this week.

20:31.106 --> 20:32.644
Just you and me.
How 'bout that?

20:32.933 --> 20:34.245
Why?

20:34.488 --> 20:35.823
Why?

20:35.917 --> 20:38.198
'Cause I'm your dad
and I want to, that's why.

20:38.636 --> 20:40.409
- Okay.
- Okay.

20:44.667 --> 20:46.292
Come on.

20:47.760 --> 20:49.689
Sorry this is so last minute.
I won't make a habit out of it.

20:49.714 --> 20:51.026
I don't mind.
See you tomorrow.

20:51.051 --> 20:52.730
Okay.

20:59.425 --> 21:00.581
Javi.

21:02.800 --> 21:04.468
Where?

21:09.522 --> 21:13.331
♪♪

21:17.458 --> 21:18.989
All right, you guys go wait
over there.

21:19.014 --> 21:20.980
Don't touch anything.
Come on.

21:29.275 --> 21:31.284
The cops don't know anything.

21:31.553 --> 21:33.995
If they did, you'd already
be in cuffs.

21:34.254 --> 21:36.448
What if they arrest baz?

21:39.513 --> 21:42.081
Are they gonna find a body?

21:44.690 --> 21:48.393
Then we don't have anything
to worry about, do we?

21:58.548 --> 22:01.089
Hey, no one will tell me
anything.

22:02.056 --> 22:05.136
What are we doing here?
What... what are the tools for?

22:09.658 --> 22:11.245
Yeah.

22:21.698 --> 22:23.714
You know, I went for
Smurf's gun.

22:23.997 --> 22:25.238
And I would've used it.

22:25.310 --> 22:28.495
I just couldn't figure out
how to load it.

22:32.071 --> 22:34.683
I never want to feel
like that again.

22:47.666 --> 22:48.800
Hey.

22:48.964 --> 22:50.076
You remember
when we were kids,

22:50.100 --> 22:51.767
we used to fight over
the game boy?

22:52.099 --> 22:54.070
Smurf would make us hit
each other over and over again

22:54.094 --> 22:56.519
- till one of us quit?
- Yeah.

22:56.778 --> 22:58.691
I always used to kick your ass.

22:59.244 --> 23:01.619
Uh, you were scrappy.

23:02.369 --> 23:04.222
No, you were huge,
even when you were 6.

23:04.270 --> 23:05.722
You used to let me win.

23:06.855 --> 23:08.160
Didn't wanna kill you.

23:08.341 --> 23:09.824
Smurf would get so pissed.

23:09.889 --> 23:11.652
She thought I'd never learn
how to fight.

23:11.879 --> 23:13.979
She'd sic pope on you.

23:15.660 --> 23:17.925
Well, don't feel bad.

23:18.821 --> 23:21.105
I was bigger than him, too.

23:23.432 --> 23:25.323
It's funny, you know, smurf is
always talking about

23:25.347 --> 23:27.550
how we have to
have each other's backs.

23:29.788 --> 23:31.788
But she loved when we fought.

23:32.191 --> 23:33.363
Yeah.

23:35.417 --> 23:36.768
It's Nico.

23:39.947 --> 23:42.003
Hey. What's up, man? We good?

23:42.128 --> 23:44.394
- It's in the alley.
- All right, let's go.

23:45.409 --> 23:46.640
Uniforms?

23:46.705 --> 23:48.824
- In the back.
- All right.

23:49.269 --> 23:50.835
All right, so we'll
drop the car off

23:50.878 --> 23:52.956
at the airport
long-term parking.

23:53.036 --> 23:54.730
You can pick it up
tomorrow morning, okay?

23:54.871 --> 23:57.667
All right, look,
no blood in my truck.

23:58.491 --> 24:01.659
- Just picking up some old shit.
- Thanks, Nico.

24:01.730 --> 24:03.425
Got a couple more things to do
in the office,

24:03.449 --> 24:04.878
then we'll get out of here,
okay?

24:05.109 --> 24:06.776
All right.

24:07.976 --> 24:10.210
Okay, so the bullets
are in the clip.

24:10.603 --> 24:11.996
Wanna push that in there...

24:12.020 --> 24:13.831
- all the way until it clicks. Okay.
- Mm-hmm.

24:13.855 --> 24:15.417
All right, now...

24:17.745 --> 24:19.050
Pull it up.

24:20.316 --> 24:22.355
Keep your finger
on the side there.

24:23.282 --> 24:25.863
Okay, now you're gonna wanna
pull back the hammer.

24:27.152 --> 24:29.542
A bit harder.
There you go.

24:30.057 --> 24:32.527
Okay, now that's ready to fire,
so be careful.

24:33.271 --> 24:35.339
Well, how do I aim it?

24:37.831 --> 24:39.066
See these white dots?

24:39.132 --> 24:41.566
Mm-hmm.
You wanna line those up

24:41.660 --> 24:43.735
right where
you wanna shoot, okay?

24:43.792 --> 24:45.191
Bring your elbows in,

24:45.271 --> 24:47.456
turn your body to the side
a little bit.

24:47.671 --> 24:49.027
There you go.

24:49.219 --> 24:52.688
And then,
when you're ready,

24:52.846 --> 24:55.378
you just keep firing
until the clip runs out.

24:57.542 --> 24:58.878
Thank you.

24:59.742 --> 25:02.074
Don't let Deran
see that in here.

25:03.518 --> 25:06.370
Put it away. We gotta go.

25:15.808 --> 25:18.988
- That's the one.
- Are you sure?

25:19.170 --> 25:20.949
I haven't been here
in 20 years.

25:20.996 --> 25:23.096
I wasn't expecting to
come back, either.

25:23.168 --> 25:26.160
We're not going in
unless you're sure.

25:32.818 --> 25:36.488
♪♪

25:38.056 --> 25:39.683
That's it. That's the one.

25:39.918 --> 25:41.425
It's right next to
the drainage ditch

25:41.503 --> 25:43.191
on the southeast side
of the street.

25:43.354 --> 25:45.167
Whose idea was this place?

25:45.370 --> 25:46.886
Jake's.

25:47.561 --> 25:49.925
He was working some construction
in the neighborhood

25:50.003 --> 25:52.722
and he knew they were
pouring foundation.

25:54.480 --> 25:56.894
I thought <i> you</i> ran that crew.

26:00.925 --> 26:02.675
Manny shot him,

26:04.248 --> 26:05.848
Jake buried him,

26:06.667 --> 26:08.410
and you just...

26:09.244 --> 26:10.792
Watched?

26:11.591 --> 26:15.042
♪♪

26:39.084 --> 26:41.123
I'm sorry to hear about Julia.

26:44.180 --> 26:46.664
What the hell are you doing,
Javi?

26:48.460 --> 26:50.414
You remember this place?

26:51.775 --> 26:54.367
We used to smoke
a lot of shit down here.

26:54.734 --> 26:56.320
You, me, and pope.

26:56.775 --> 26:58.437
Yeah, I remember.

27:00.806 --> 27:02.797
She tell you about my dad?

27:04.654 --> 27:06.601
Yeah, she did.

27:08.093 --> 27:09.789
What'd she say?

27:10.042 --> 27:11.812
That Manny did it?

27:16.997 --> 27:19.273
She shot him
in the back of the head,

27:19.787 --> 27:22.398
then threw his body in a hole,
and then told me my dad was

27:22.492 --> 27:25.242
a piece of shit
who ran out on me.

27:28.659 --> 27:30.633
Okay, so what do you want
to do about it?

27:30.703 --> 27:33.797
You wanna kill her? 'Cause we're
never gonna let that happen.

27:34.234 --> 27:37.836
So if you want something else,
let's start negotiating.

27:40.138 --> 27:41.976
Man, you know,

27:43.551 --> 27:46.664
every birthday, Christmas,

27:46.848 --> 27:48.547
I thought, "oh, this is it.

27:48.721 --> 27:51.195
This is the year
my dad comes back for me."

27:52.062 --> 27:53.557
And I thought
'cause she took you in,

27:53.609 --> 27:55.765
she'd take me in, too.

27:57.305 --> 28:01.065
Bro, I spent the last 20 years
wiping Manny's ass

28:01.187 --> 28:02.633
and doing small-time 211's

28:02.658 --> 28:04.241
in the middle
of Goddamn nowhere.

28:05.804 --> 28:07.989
You know and smurf seems like
she's just doing fine, man,

28:08.013 --> 28:10.476
like she didn't lose
no sleep.

28:12.549 --> 28:14.796
So do you wanna go back
to Arizona with nothing,

28:14.869 --> 28:16.608
or do you wanna get paid?

28:16.834 --> 28:18.601
I already tried.

28:19.013 --> 28:21.213
I asked for money.
She didn't show.

28:21.348 --> 28:23.403
She's not running things
anymore.

28:23.850 --> 28:25.550
I can get you the money.

28:25.817 --> 28:26.942
Hmm.

28:27.637 --> 28:30.434
Keys to the kingdom, huh?

28:31.164 --> 28:32.934
How does pope feel
about that?

28:33.226 --> 28:35.300
Well, he doesn't feel great
about you threatening smurf,

28:35.324 --> 28:36.512
I'll tell you that.

28:36.988 --> 28:39.090
Look, you took 25 from
the house.

28:39.169 --> 28:41.770
It's gonna cost at least 10
to fix the wall,

28:42.059 --> 28:44.910
plus the bullshit with
the kid and the girlfriend.

28:45.418 --> 28:48.219
- Let's call it 200.
- No, no, 400.

28:48.504 --> 28:49.973
She doesn't wanna give you
anything.

28:50.060 --> 28:52.481
Dude, I can't go back to my crew
with 200. Come on.

28:52.587 --> 28:54.121
I'm trying
to help you here, man.

28:54.310 --> 28:57.317
It's 200 or it's nothing.
Those are your choices.

28:57.699 --> 28:59.824
What do you wanna do?

29:01.059 --> 29:04.695
You remember when your dad used
to get loaded

29:04.697 --> 29:07.264
and kick the shit out of you
in front of Smurf's yard?

29:10.145 --> 29:13.215
Man, you've come a long way
from crying yourself to sleep

29:13.340 --> 29:15.192
and pissing the bed, man.

29:17.215 --> 29:18.809
Good for you.

29:19.934 --> 29:22.598
'Cause, you know, shit didn't
turn out so well for me

29:22.970 --> 29:24.503
or my dad.

29:24.684 --> 29:26.684
♪♪

29:26.930 --> 29:28.418
It's all right.

29:29.096 --> 29:31.067
You know, Manny used to
always say that

29:31.098 --> 29:32.840
smurf would climb over
her own kids

29:32.887 --> 29:35.035
just to keep from drowning.

29:36.098 --> 29:39.043
Be careful, bro.
That's all I'm saying.

29:39.632 --> 29:41.504
You're not even her kid.

29:41.901 --> 29:45.160
♪♪

29:47.653 --> 29:49.654
So we have a deal?

29:56.716 --> 29:59.950
♪♪

30:00.066 --> 30:01.504
Good.

30:07.106 --> 30:09.387
The body's buried
along the back wall.

30:09.426 --> 30:12.738
- How deep did you bury it?
- Just about 2 or 3 inches.

30:12.988 --> 30:14.981
We thought the concrete
would save us,

30:15.065 --> 30:16.698
and we didn't have
that much time.

30:16.762 --> 30:18.089
The gun with it?

30:18.160 --> 30:19.598
- Should be.
- <i>Should</i> be?

30:19.723 --> 30:21.207
It is.

30:26.668 --> 30:30.004
I'm sorry, baby. Would you give
us another second, please?

30:30.613 --> 30:32.204
I'm not stupid.

30:32.293 --> 30:34.934
I know who you are.
I know what you do.

30:35.309 --> 30:36.473
You're right.

30:36.564 --> 30:38.063
You're a smart girl.

30:38.300 --> 30:40.567
And we should tell you
the truth.

30:40.840 --> 30:42.004
Thanks.

30:42.513 --> 30:45.080
But not now. Next time.

30:45.707 --> 30:48.809
Now do you have someplace else
you can sleep tonight?

30:49.270 --> 30:51.551
- Yeah.
- Okay, go get packed.

30:53.558 --> 30:54.730
Tools?

30:54.832 --> 30:56.633
- Yeah.
- Truck?

30:56.855 --> 30:58.425
Parked it down the street.

30:59.655 --> 31:00.824
You gotta pay Javi.

31:00.992 --> 31:03.582
200 instead of 300
because of what he did to j.

31:03.723 --> 31:05.612
I know you don't like it,
and you don't have to,

31:05.637 --> 31:07.645
but it's what we gotta do
right now. I'm sorry.

31:08.731 --> 31:10.668
And that's fair, smurf.

31:11.755 --> 31:13.455
You owe him.

31:14.136 --> 31:15.582
Okay.

31:15.910 --> 31:17.356
When?

31:18.252 --> 31:19.652
Two hours.

31:20.411 --> 31:21.840
Smart.

31:22.324 --> 31:24.840
All right, let's go.
I'll meet you at the Van.

31:41.059 --> 31:43.199
Are you sure
you should go with her?

31:43.887 --> 31:45.738
She's not going alone.

31:46.052 --> 31:48.119
What about the cops?

31:49.888 --> 31:52.155
- If I get a tail, I'll lose it.
- Yeah.

31:52.354 --> 31:54.505
- Good luck.
- You, too.

32:02.462 --> 32:05.464
So where'd you get the money
to pay Javi?

32:06.472 --> 32:08.181
I told you. My savings.

32:08.206 --> 32:10.431
Mm, that's bullshit.

32:11.004 --> 32:12.884
You've been skimming off
our work.

32:13.165 --> 32:15.939
I'm the only one in this family
who can see past

32:16.025 --> 32:18.205
the next Goddamn party.

32:19.736 --> 32:22.494
Okay. Great,
so time to dip back in.

32:22.712 --> 32:25.283
Do I drive you to a bank?
How does it work?

32:27.053 --> 32:29.970
You really think I have more,
don't you?

32:31.009 --> 32:36.461
Jake took everything I have,
and Javi cleaned out this house.

32:38.384 --> 32:43.301
Well, didn't you boys just come
into a bit of church money?

32:43.806 --> 32:45.470
Smurf, you gotta
be kidding me.

32:45.688 --> 32:47.298
Well, we could show up
with nothing

32:47.400 --> 32:48.970
and see how he takes it.

32:50.228 --> 32:52.470
You're paying me back before
they know it's gone.

32:52.580 --> 32:55.283
If you have to sell the house,
you're gonna do it.

32:55.616 --> 32:59.330
♪♪

33:02.388 --> 33:06.048
♪♪

33:26.154 --> 33:27.720
Let's go.

33:41.745 --> 33:45.047
♪♪

34:17.793 --> 34:19.723
Hi.
Good afternoon, ma'am.

34:19.774 --> 34:22.254
Uh, there were reports
of a gas leak in the area.

34:22.559 --> 34:24.129
We have to ask you to leave

34:24.168 --> 34:26.567
while we make sure
everything's okay.

34:32.945 --> 34:36.328
The bruises will get worse
before they get better.

34:38.639 --> 34:42.031
And you're gonna need
proper stitches in that leg.

34:42.522 --> 34:44.617
I can do it for you,
if you want.

34:45.038 --> 34:46.484
It's up to you.

34:55.742 --> 34:58.312
I know you think
we should kill him.

35:00.398 --> 35:02.774
But have you ever hurt
somebody?

35:05.460 --> 35:07.361
Really hurt them?

35:10.265 --> 35:12.640
Doesn't feel like
you think it will.

35:20.726 --> 35:22.093
Thank you.

35:26.532 --> 35:30.196
♪♪

35:35.162 --> 35:37.776
Down there on the left.
I'll get the tools.

35:47.848 --> 35:49.590
Got a new car?

35:50.231 --> 35:54.168
It's a loaner. Challenger
needs a new transmission.

35:55.809 --> 36:00.365
Baz, how do you know we're not
driving straight into an ambush?

36:01.760 --> 36:03.410
He'll take the money.

36:03.703 --> 36:06.805
♪♪

36:10.142 --> 36:11.918
Somebody following us?

36:12.403 --> 36:15.020
Just being careful.

36:22.588 --> 36:26.301
♪♪

36:32.631 --> 36:36.301
♪♪

36:50.710 --> 36:54.582
♪♪

37:07.527 --> 37:09.128
Yeah, pipe.

37:20.854 --> 37:22.791
Bingo. Pipe.

37:31.529 --> 37:32.615
We got a hit.

37:32.650 --> 37:34.155
Gun.

37:38.433 --> 37:41.134
Shit, how much gas
did you guys pour in here?

37:42.097 --> 37:44.504
All right, let's tear it up.

37:53.547 --> 37:56.855
♪♪

38:13.855 --> 38:17.308
♪♪

38:33.120 --> 38:36.122
♪♪

38:36.756 --> 38:38.423
Stop.

38:40.694 --> 38:44.430
♪♪

39:10.264 --> 39:12.304
What's going on here?

39:16.272 --> 39:17.858
Wait here.

39:20.813 --> 39:22.483
What's he doing here?

39:22.862 --> 39:24.530
Hey, there's two of you.

39:24.690 --> 39:26.382
Are we gonna have a problem?

39:26.608 --> 39:28.257
Why don't you tell her
to get out of the car?

39:28.281 --> 39:29.773
Javi...

39:30.020 --> 39:32.187
Got your money right here.

39:33.540 --> 39:34.907
I wanna talk with her.

39:35.089 --> 39:38.241
Javi, your dad's been dead
for 20 years.

39:38.608 --> 39:42.218
She is never gonna say
she's sorry.

39:42.819 --> 39:44.485
Take the money.

39:48.208 --> 39:51.804
♪♪

40:10.084 --> 40:13.386
♪♪

40:26.823 --> 40:28.175
Gun.

40:29.037 --> 40:30.096
That's it.

40:30.233 --> 40:32.266
What, did this guy only have
one foot?

40:32.471 --> 40:34.073
We're missing one.

40:35.542 --> 40:36.843
Shit.

40:45.260 --> 40:46.534
Man, it's not here.

40:46.691 --> 40:48.090
Keep digging.

40:49.419 --> 40:51.479
Look, man,
we have the gun.

40:51.925 --> 40:52.995
Huh?

40:53.059 --> 40:55.393
We're not leaving without
a Goddamn foot.

40:55.642 --> 40:57.909
Get out of the way.

40:59.644 --> 41:01.778
♪♪

41:03.279 --> 41:05.292
I don't know.
He said I had to leave.

41:05.797 --> 41:07.314
Guys, we
got a bunch of neighbors

41:07.364 --> 41:09.184
<i>on the front lawn, asking questions.</i>

41:09.600 --> 41:11.026
Pope.

41:13.110 --> 41:15.057
What do you want me to do?

41:16.688 --> 41:18.548
Maybe it's not even here.

41:19.047 --> 41:20.931
It's gotta be there.
Where else could it be?

41:20.964 --> 41:24.448
I'm telling you, cops aren't
going to ID a foot.

41:24.854 --> 41:26.385
Let's just leave it.

41:27.456 --> 41:28.620
Shut up.

41:28.714 --> 41:30.924
<i>Okay, well, we got about
15 minutes before the old lady</i>

41:30.948 --> 41:32.871
calls dispatch and finds out
there's no leak.

41:34.082 --> 41:37.134
I'm moving as fast as I can.

41:38.414 --> 41:39.589
Wait.

41:39.749 --> 41:41.190
Hey, is that it?

41:41.318 --> 41:42.495
There we go.

41:42.552 --> 41:44.253
Good job, bro.

41:44.823 --> 41:46.651
Let's get
the hell outta here.

41:46.776 --> 41:49.657
♪♪

41:49.893 --> 41:51.259
Got it?

42:04.114 --> 42:06.489
- Javi?
- Get out of here. Go.

42:09.489 --> 42:12.512
I really do owe you
an explanation, huh?

42:12.973 --> 42:16.918
You know all that bullshit
about me not having any room?

42:17.121 --> 42:18.731
That was just silly.

42:21.520 --> 42:25.535
I didn't take you in
because you were <i> worthless.</i>

42:26.340 --> 42:29.473
You were stupid and angry

42:29.621 --> 42:31.733
and impulsive,

42:32.223 --> 42:34.200
just like your father.

42:38.098 --> 42:39.457
Goddamn...

42:42.621 --> 42:45.366
Jesus Christ.

42:48.550 --> 42:51.973
♪♪

43:08.267 --> 43:10.772
Bury the body over the fence.

43:12.923 --> 43:14.853
Get rid of your gun.

43:15.392 --> 43:16.644
Here you go.

43:17.087 --> 43:18.413
That's it.

43:18.486 --> 43:20.298
That's all you're getting.

43:20.860 --> 43:22.096
Is that all in there?

43:22.185 --> 43:23.673
It's there.

43:23.861 --> 43:26.687
The other 50 is in a building
on ventura.

43:26.853 --> 43:29.986
It's called the Lisbon.
Mailbox 5c.

43:30.126 --> 43:31.837
Get it out of there tonight,

43:32.009 --> 43:34.540
and get yourself
out of California.

43:37.366 --> 43:40.775
♪♪

44:07.171 --> 44:08.825
Well, we're all done in there.

44:08.974 --> 44:11.489
We had to, uh, dig up part of
the floor to get to the pipe.

44:11.606 --> 44:13.224
But, uh, dispatch will
give you a call,

44:13.286 --> 44:15.255
send someone out
to patch it up.

44:15.388 --> 44:18.013
But thank you so much.
You've been very kind.

44:50.708 --> 44:53.075
Don't expect me to help you
when this comes back to bite us!

44:53.185 --> 44:54.851
I'm not doing it!

44:56.341 --> 44:58.481
You wouldn't do what needed
to be done.

44:58.606 --> 44:59.763
I found someone who would.

44:59.824 --> 45:02.575
We have the body!
He was gonna take the money!

45:03.122 --> 45:04.819
I mean, what?!

